<div id="header">
<h1>Polyvariance</h1>
</div>
<div id="content">
<div id="preamble">
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>Polyvariance is an optimization pass for the <a href="SXML">SXML</a>
<a href="IntermediateLanguage">IntermediateLanguage</a>, invoked from <a href="SXMLSimplify">SXMLSimplify</a>.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
<div class="sect1">
<h2 id="_description">Description</h2>
<div class="sectionbody">
<div class="paragraph">
<p>This pass duplicates a higher-order, <code>let</code> bound function at each
variable reference, if the cost is smaller than some threshold.</p>
</div>
</div>
</div>
